Version:    1.5.0

Releases:   https://github.com/mdbootstrap/perfect-scrollbar/releases

Homepage:   https://github.com/mdbootstrap/perfect-scrollbar

Notes:      perfect-scrollbar.min.js:

                - Copy /dist/perfect-scrollbar.min.js

            perfect-scrollbar.css:

                - Copy /dist/perfect-scrollbar.css
                - Rename it to perfect-scrollbar.scss
                    (This file is included in our main scss file: '__scss/style.scss'.

                    Update:
                        - Find: "border-radius: 6px;"     -> Replace: "border-radius: 1px;"          (2x)
                        - Find: "background-color: #aaa;" -> Replace: "background-color: #f3f3fa;"   (2x)
                        - Find: "background-color: #999;" -> Replace: "background-color: #f3f3fa;"   (2x)
                        - Find: "opacity: 0.6;"           -> Replace: "opacity: 0.2;"                (1x)
                        - Find: "background-color: #eee;" -> Replace: "/*background-color: #eee;*/"  (1x)

                - The .css is not used, the .scss is important


            The .map are only included for Chrome dev tools, so it does not complain about "DevTools failed to parse SourceMap:"
            They have no other purpose, get them via the /dist/ directory.
            Can maybe be removed later on, when this message disapears again.